      <data key="d5">pcie (pci express) / pci-sig</data>
      <data key="d7">Serial high-speed I/O interconnect standard. CXL reuses PCIe's electrical layer (Flex Bus), transaction layer framing, and Data Link Layer (DLL) for CXL.io. Subject to alternate protocol negotiation via APN to switch between PCIe and CXL modes.</data>
